Introduction

Wonhee is a South Korean singer under Belift Lab. She is the center and lead vocalist of the South Korean girl group ILLIT.

In June 2023, she participated in HYBE and Belift Lab's survival show called R U Next?, where she was chosen by fans' votes as the first member to debut in the final group ILLIT.
